
'''
        DATASET INFORMATION 

        Description of the features and targets of the models, described in order of column index. 

        Features:       Plan_Area               ;   Float - Plan area of structure
                        Volume	                ;   Float - Volume of individual object (0 for object N/A)
                        Surface_Area	        ;   Float - Surface area of individual object (0 for object N/A)
                        BB_x	                ;   Float - Length of object (Bounding Box)
                        BB_y	                ;   Float - Width of object (Bounding Box)
                        BB_z	                ;   Float - Depth of object (Bounding Box)
                        Min_z	                ;   Float - Lowest elevation of object
                        Max_z	                ;   Float - Highest elevation of object
                        Apect_Ratio_xy	        ;   Float - BB_x / BB_y
                        Aspect_Ratio_Z	        ;   Float - BB_z / MAX(BB_x, BB_y)
                        Thickness_Proxy	        ;   Float - Volume / Surface_Area
                        Density	                ;   Float - Density of object material 
                        No_faces	            ;   Int - Number of object faces (curved and planar)
                        is_WetTrade	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if wet trade required
                        is_HotTrade	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if hot trade required
                        Is_SurfaceConstruction	;   Binary Int - 1/0 if surface construction required
                        is_collective	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object part of a collection (e.g. truss)
                        is_prefabricated	    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is prefabricated
                        No_dependance	        ;   Int - Number of other objects this object relies on (by physics)
                        No_dependants	        ;   Int - Number of other objects that rely on this object (by physics)
                        Has_Predceding_Access	;   Binary Int - 1/0 if there is stairs/ramps leading to this object when constructed
                        Storey	                ;   Int - Storey of the object (-1 for foundations, 0,1,2,3... otherwise)
                        is_installed	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is a off-shelf unit to be installed (e.g. windows)
                        Relative_elevation	    ;   Float - Max_z / Total structure's height
                        Is_edge_object	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is on the perimeter of the structure
                        is_masonry	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is masonry
                        is_steel	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is steel
                        is_Composite	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is composite
                        is_concrete	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is concrete
                        is_rock	                ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is rock
                        is_timber               ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if object is timber

        Targets:        Scaffolding_needed	                ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if scaffolding was needed for object's construction
                        Pre_Construction_proccess_time	    ;   Float - time to carry out pre-construction tasks for object
                        Construction_proccess_time	        ;   Float - time to carry out construction tasks for object
                        Post_Construction_proccess_time	    ;   Float - time to carry out post-construction tasks for object
                        Curing_time	                        ;   Float - time to carry out curing for object
                        is_formwork	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if formwork is required
                        is_decking	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if decking is required
                        is_temporary_support	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if temporary support/s is required
                        is_reinforcement_install	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if reinforcement tying is required
                        is_excavation	                    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if excavation is required
                        is_substrate_prep	                ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if substrate preparation is required
                        is_fastened	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object is fastened
                        is_welded	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object is welded
                        is_lap_splicing	                    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object is lap spliced, or splicing required
                        is_grouted	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object is grouted
                        is_install_connections	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the connections must be installed for the object
                        is_gravity_supported	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object is supported without connections
                        construction_proccess	            ;   Catagorical Int   - 0: Placement
                                                                                    1: Installation
                                                                                    2: Assembley
                                                                                    3: Casting
                                                                                    4: Applying
                                                                                    5: Laying
                                                                                    6: Piling
                        is_sealing	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object has sealant applied
                        is_installing_products	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object must have products installed to it
                        is_tensioning	                    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object must have tensioning carried out
                        is_surface_finishing	            ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object must have surface products (e.g. paint) applied
                        is_curing	                        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object must cure
                        is_formwork_removal	                ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the formwork must be removed
                        post_Edge_protection_needed	        ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if post-construction edge protection is needed on site
                        is_temporary_support_removal	    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object's temporary support must be removed
                        is_backfilling	                    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if backfiling is required
                        is_inspecting	                    ;   Binary Int - 1/0 if the object must be inspected 
                        Lifting_type                        ;   Catagorical Int  -  0: None
                                                                                    1: Manual
                                                                                    2: Hoist
                                                                                    3: Mobile Crane
                                                                                    4: Tower Crane
                                                                                    5: Forklift
                                                                                    6: Telehandler
                                                                                    7: Truck    

        
        Regression model: 
            Will return the float targets (Pre_Construction_proccess_time, Construction_proccess_time, 
            Post_Construction_proccess_time and Curing_time). 
        
        Classification model:
            Will return all other targets (binary and catagorical).

'''

